## Task Manager and Resource Monitor
These tools provide real‑time insight into running processes and resource consumption.

Tasks performed
- Opened Task Manager to review active processes.
- Used Resource Monitor for detailed CPU, disk, and network activity.
- Verified that AD DS and DNS services are running.

Expected results
- Domain Controller services (e.g., lsass.exe, dns.exe) are active.
- No unexpected processes consuming excessive resources.

