## Active Directory Administrative Tools
Windows Server provides several AD‑specific tools for managing and monitoring domain components.

Tools reviewed
- Active Directory Users and Computers (ADUC)
Used to manage users, groups, and OUs.
- Active Directory Sites and Services
Used to verify Domain Controller status and replication.
- Active Directory Domains and Trusts
Used to manage domain and forest functional levels.
- DNS Manager
Used to monitor DNS zones and records.

Expected results
- Domain Controller appears healthy in Sites and Services.
- DNS zones contain correct records.
- No replication errors (single‑DC environment).

