## dcdiag and repadmin (Command‑Line Tools)
These tools provide deeper diagnostics for AD DS.

Tasks performed
- Ran dcdiag to check domain controller health.
- Ran repadmin /replsummary (even though replication is minimal in a single‑DC environment).
Example commands

```
dcdiag /v
repadmin /replsummary
```

Expected results
- dcdiag reports no critical errors.
- repadmin shows no replication issues.

