## Summary
Monitoring and administrative tools in Windows Server 2012 provide essential visibility into the health and performance of the szkola.local domain. Event Viewer, Performance Monitor, AD tools, and command‑line diagnostics help ensure that the Domain Controller, DNS, and client systems operate reliably. With these tools, administrators can quickly identify issues, verify configuration, and maintain a stable school domain environment.